{"id":1735200,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:22.654Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735200,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Love You Mr Arang","overview":"# Love You Mr. Arang  The story follows Irma (Hanna Aqeela) who is pressured by her mother to marry as quickly as possible. Irma is very stressed because she needs to find a life partner in a short time to avoid marrying her mother's choice. Irma says that she already has her own choice of heart. After meeting, her choice does not meet her mother's criteria at all. Irma's mother, Datuk Sherry (Maria Farida), who dreams of having a fair-skinned and pale daughter-in-law, is completely disappointed when Irma introduces her prospective husband, Fariz (Amirul Faqeem). Unsatisfied with Irma's choice, Datuk Sherry continues to call the dark-skinned Fariz \"Mr. Charcoal.\" Fariz comes from a village and is the breadwinner for his family. One day, Fariz accidentally hits Irma's car. Irma immediately rages and demands compensation of RM 5,000. Fariz is shocked to be scolded by Irma even though it was his fault. For Fariz, his dignity feels tarnished and his ego is challenged.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/fyk00Q3WDzxl22EksjHJ2ANB0ch.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2016-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Love You Mr Arang","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2385179,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Amirul Faqeem","original_name":"Amirul Faqeem","popularity":0.2352,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5ee75d130d9c0a5f4ac373","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2146084,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Hanna Aqeela","original_name":"Han